i><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\">当事件被<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Reference/Events/abort_(cancellable_fetch)\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">终止</a></code>，<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>FetchSignal</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>接口的<strong><code>onabort</code></strong>&nbsp;只读属性就会被调用。例子。当 fetch 的请求信号被终止。</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>abortSignal<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onabort</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>在下面例子中，我们将创建一个新的&nbsp;<code>AbortController</code> 对象，并获取它的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>AbortSignal</code></a> (在&nbsp;<code>signal</code> 属性中可用)。然后我们查看 <code>onabort</code> 属性是否被终止，并将相应的日志输出到控制台。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> controller <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">AbortController</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> signal <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> controller<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>signal<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nsignal<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onabort</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Request aborted'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规格","id":"规格","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#eventdef-abortsignal-abort","title":"DOM Standard"},{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#abortsignal-onabort","title":"DOM Standard"}],"query":"api.AbortSignal.abort_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.AbortSignal.onabort","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参考文档","title":"参考文档","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Fetch_API\">Fetch API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规格","id":"规格"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参考文档","id":"参考文档"}],"summary":"在下面例子中，我们将创建一个新的 AbortController 对象，并获取它的AbortSignal (在 signal 属性中可用)。然后我们查看 onabort 属性是否被终止，并将相应的日志输出到控制台。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"AbortSignal: abort event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"abort","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/abortsignal/abort_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/abortsignal/abort_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.